<Q REND="inline margQuotes">"Spare me not <HI>becau&s;e</HI> I am your Friend; but, rather, for that very rea&s;on &s;pare me not."</Q></ITEM>
<ITEM>No true Friend can a&s;k to be relieved from a di&s;tre&s;s, which would involve a Friend in as deep a one.</ITEM>
