<ITEM>I have no notion, <HI>&s;ays Mi&s;s Howe,</HI> of coolne&s;s in Friend&s;hip, be it di&s;gui&s;ed, or di&s;tingui&s;hed, by the name of <HI>Prudence,</HI> or what it will.</ITEM>
<ITEM>It is not every one who has a &s;oul capable of Friend&s;hip.</ITEM>
